00:00:20.696 --> 00:00:21.495
What are you going to cook Mrs.Padma?

00:00:21.678 --> 00:00:22.106
Kova puri

00:00:30.625 --> 00:00:31.625
Ingredients to make kova puri:

00:00:32.554 --> 00:00:37.549
Oil, Sugar, Ghee, kova, Cashew nuts

00:00:38.206 --> 00:00:38.774
Cashew nuts powder

00:00:39.610 --> 00:00:40.082
Refined flour

00:00:39.195 --> 00:00:41.131
Salt

00:00:48.246 --> 00:00:54.737
Firstly,heat some ghee in a pan

00:00:57.150 --> 00:01:04.853
Take some refined flour &amp; add pinch of salt into it with some ghee

00:01:10.896 --> 00:01:25.295
Mix it thoroughly &amp; make a dough of it

00:01:31.399 --> 00:01:39.929
Now, take a frying pan &amp; heat some Kova into it

00:01:44.322 --> 00:02:02.689
Add the required amount of sugar into it &amp; wait till it becomes soft

00:02:04.286 --> 00:02:10.902
Mean while make the balls with the refined flour

00:02:13.145 --> 00:02:17.876
Roll the balls into thines...

00:03:10.568 --> 00:03:20.160
After the kova becomes soft, add some cashew nuts powder into it

00:03:34.302 --> 00:03:40.792
Mix it properly &amp; take it in a bowl

00:03:47.475 --> 00:03:52.821
Now, heat some oil in the same pan

00:04:04.630 --> 00:04:10.632
Spread the batter on the thine

00:04:20.463 --> 00:04:23.516
Dip your finger in the water &amp; slightly rub it on the edges of the thine

00:04:25.932 --> 00:04:28.058
Place another thine over it

00:04:29.043 --> 00:04:33.060
Cut the thines in a round shape

00:04:34.121 --> 00:04:35.300
Remove the edges...

00:04:37.656 --> 00:04:41.655
Seal the edges of the sandwiched thines

00:04:55.229 --> 00:05:10.774
Deep fry the thines till the colour turns golden brown

00:05:12.498 --> 00:05:14.086
Kova puri is ready to serve...!!!

00:05:18.351 --> 00:05:19.967
Superb...!!!

